      "title": "Building a Community-Based Collaborative Learning System Using Multi-Agent",
      "abstract": "The paper presents a system that using multi-agent technology to organize and reorganize supportive communities based on learners. Through effective award and exchange algorithms, learners with similar interests and experiences form a community to support each others’ learning."
